00:40:03.600 --> 00:40:06.050 align:middle line:84%
But one of the
things when you say

00:40:06.050 --> 00:40:08.570 align:middle line:84%
this-- when you say we have
to get used to the notion

00:40:08.570 --> 00:40:12.890 align:middle line:84%
that maybe the ultimate of the
development of conscious beings

00:40:12.890 --> 00:40:15.410 align:middle line:84%
on the planet isn't
human and we need

00:40:15.410 --> 00:40:19.950 align:middle line:84%
to support the flowering of
