00:40:19.950 --> 00:40:20.750 align:middle line:90%
is true.

00:40:20.750 --> 00:40:23.570 align:middle line:84%
But I think people then
become frightened thinking

00:40:23.570 --> 00:40:25.410 align:middle line:90%
we're not it.

00:40:25.410 --> 00:40:28.160 align:middle line:84%
But what I want to say
is it doesn't matter.

00:40:28.160 --> 00:40:29.700 align:middle line:90%
Our consciousness continues.

00:40:29.700 --> 00:40:30.500 align:middle line:90%
>>STRAND: Yes.

00:40:30.500 --> 00:40:31.417 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: We continue.

00:40:31.417 --> 00:40:32.780 align:middle line:90%
We can go to another place.

00:40:32.780 --> 00:40:36.380 align:middle line:84%
We can take a human form again
somewhere else if that happens.

00:40:36.380 --> 00:40:39.500 align:middle line:84%
Now, that's not an advertisement
to allow what's happening

00:40:39.500 --> 00:40:41.250 align:middle line:90%
to our ecosystems happen.

00:40:41.250 --> 00:40:42.300 align:middle line:90%
I'm not saying that.

00:40:42.300 --> 00:40:45.500 align:middle line:84%
I'm saying not to go
into fear over the fact

00:40:45.500 --> 00:40:49.650 align:middle line:84%
that one will cease to
exist if humans went by the

00:40:49.650 --> 00:40:51.740 align:middle line:90%
by on this particular planet.

00:40:51.740 --> 00:40:53.880 align:middle line:90%
Even that's not a disaster.

00:40:53.880 --> 00:40:56.150 align:middle line:84%
There are other places
