00:40:56.150 --> 00:40:58.820 align:middle line:84%
other forms to
express oneself in.

00:40:58.820 --> 00:41:00.740 align:middle line:90%
>>STRAND: That's very beautiful.

00:41:00.740 --> 00:41:03.800 align:middle line:84%
